The [[Dread Buccaneer]] '''Hez Kragg''' was an infamous [[Realspace/Legends|space]] [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] during the time of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]]. He became so legendary that his adventures were told as a fable to children, until evidence proving his existence surfaced during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

His [[Flagship/Legends|flagship]] was ''[[Kragg's Fury]]'', which he left booby-trapped in order to challenge any profiteers that came across his final resting place.

Kraggs' symbol was a [[Color/Legends|crimson]] fist set upon a circle of gold.

